Value = Base Ã— Rarity Ã— Quality Ã— (1 + Attributes) Ã— (1 + Sales) 

This formula mimics natural market growth:
- Scarcity (rarity)
- Craftsmanship (quality)
- Uniqueness (attributes)
- Reputation (sales)

---

## Gameplay & Economics

### Crafting
To mint (craft) an NFT:
1. Spend `componentCost` in ERC20 tokens.
2. Tokens are burned, ensuring scarcity.
3. A new NFT is minted with randomized quality and chosen attributes.

### Selling
Trusted marketplaces can call `recordSale(tokenId)` to increase its `sellCount`, which in turn **boosts its computed value**.

